### Restaurant Management API - Test Requests

### 1. Create Restaurant
POST https://localhost:5001/api/restaurants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Italian Bistro",
  "tableCount": 15,
  "allergyTags": "gluten,lactose,nuts,shellfish",
  "dietTags": "vegan,vegetarian,halal,kosher"
}

###

### 2. Get All Restaurants
GET https://localhost:5001/api/restaurants

###

### 3. Get Restaurant by ID
GET https://localhost:5001/api/restaurants/1

###

### 4. Create Menu Item
POST https://localhost:5001/api/menuitems
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Margherita Pizza",
  "description": "Classic Italian pizza with tomato sauce and mozzarella",
  "price": 12.99,
  "category": "Main Course",
  "allergens": "gluten,lactose",
  "dietaryInfo": "vegetarian",
  "restaurantId": 1,
  "isAvailable": true
}

###

### 5. Create Another Menu Item
